S.FORM: alang Qyuws ga niya mki sku Sincik Keng atu Nahuy go, kwara sali buwan nya ga 88 buwan, 399 hi ku kwara s'uli tayan. s'uli tayan pinspngan Gyencumin ga 95% kyan ku 379 hi, binah ga, 'yat kahun sku pinspngan Gyencumin ga 5% kyan ku 20 hi nya. pinspung na linhuyan Gyencumin ga, Tayan 92%, Amis 0.5%, Rukay 0.5%, binah lihuyan s'uli 2%. maki qu ngasal bziran. rhzyal kki'an tay 'llaw na Qyuws hya' ga llyung. tay 'zil na Qyuws hya' ga rgyax krahu'. tay mkyahu' na Qyuws hya' ga rgyax krahu'. tay mkraya' na Qyuws hya' ga rgyax krahu'. tay mkraya' na Qyuws hya' ga Qolu. rekisi kayal kyokay ssquliq pinlpgan ppqbaqan pqwasan biru 'laqi' cikuy pqwasan biru 'laqi' mrkyas tuqi 'san basu kisya' glgan spyangan na pinbahu Ubuy qqmayh

alang Qyows ga niya mki sko Sincik Keng ato Nahoy go, kwara sali bowan nya ga 88 bowan, 399 hi ko kwara s'oli tayan. s'oli tayan pinspngan Gyencomin ga 95% kyan ko 379 hi, binah ga, 'yat kahon sko pinspngan Gyencomin ga 5% kyan ko 20 hi nya. pinspong na linhoyan Gyencomin ga, Tayan 92%, Amis 0.5%, Rokay 0.5%, binah lihoyan s'oli 2%. maki qo ngasal bziran. rhzyal kki'an tay 'llaw na Qyows hya' ga llyong. tay 'zil na Qyows hya' ga rgyax kraho'. tay mkyaho' na Qyows hya' ga rgyax kraho'. tay mkraya' na Qyows hya' ga rgyax kraho'. tay mkraya' na Qyows hya' ga Qolo. rekisi kayal kyokay ssqoliq pinlpgan ppqbaqan pqwasan biro 'laqi' cikoy pqwasan biro 'laqi' mrkyas toqi 'san baso kisya' glgan spyangan na pinbaho Uboy qqmayh
